column5: Hello  Managed to get out for opener, fished sunday thru tues and what a fishing time...   We managed to stay to the hidden areas of one of my favorite rivers and every pool had tons of fish..  here are some pics I hope you enjoy                Dave
Good job. My favourites were the beautiful little browns
Nice!!! Dmasse is always good for some good action.  Lovin the fly gear man!!!!!  Don't see enough of it at OFC!!!!
Double header - you're an ass! haha awesome pix as usual Dave!  Thanks for the report!  Cheers, UF
Great job!  Fantastic colours on those fish...
